  "subject": "Initial delivery of dmaap-prov charts",
  "commit_message": "Initial delivery of dmaap-prov charts\n\nshould deploy two pods:\n1) a private postgresql container from kubernetes/stable.\nThis will be used until PG is available from DCAEGEN2.\n2) a buscontroller container which exposes the provisioning API.\nNote this runs on ports 30242 and 30243 which were reserved in the wiki.\n\nChange-Id: I5eab3417c4e5ae99e0b7d6d53e83e1f488f28751\nSigned-off-by: Dominic Lunanuova <dgl@research.att.com>\nIssue-ID: DMAAP-117\nSigned-off-by: Dominic Lunanuova <dgl@research.att.com>\n",
